Account Deletion Instructions: Bahria Ride Share App
If you wish to permanently delete your account and remove your personal data from the Bahria Ride Share platform, please follow one of the two methods below:

Method 1: Request via WhatsApp (Recommended)
To ensure a quick and secure deletion of your profile, send a formal request via WhatsApp.

WhatsApp Number: [Insert Number Here]

Message Format:

"I am requesting the permanent deletion of my account associated with the phone number [Your Registered Number]. Please remove all my personal data from the Bahria Ride Share application database."

Method 2: Contact BUCIS Community Head
If you are unable to reach support via WhatsApp or prefer to go through official university student community channels, please contact the BUCIS Community Head.

Contact Person: BUCIS Community Head

Action: Reach out directly through the official BUCIS (Bahria University Computer Science & IT Society) communication channels or visit the society office during university hours.

Important Notes:
Irreversibility: Once an account is deleted, your ride history, ratings, and profile information cannot be recovered.

Processing Time: Account deletion requests are typically processed within 24–48 hours after verification.

Data Privacy: This process ensures compliance with data protection standards by removing your mobile number and identity from our active servers.